data.description: Gorgeous home in gated Venado Creek features upgrades galore and highly sought after Comal ISD schools. Upon entering, a study/office and dining room flank the entry and then you are lead into the grand living room with soaring ceilings, an abundance of windows and custom nooks on both sides of the fireplace. The chef's kitchen presents a massive granite kitchen island, gas range and stainless steel appliances. The master retreat overlooks the backyard with a tray ceiling and ensuite bath. Upstairs boasts a flex space currently used as a game room and second living area and the four remaining bedrooms and two full baths complete the upstairs. The backyard opens to a covered area, flagstone patio and a large, level, green lawn. Timerwood Park Elementary School is .7 miles away and the recently built Pieper Ranch Middle and Pieper High School are 3.2 miles.
